],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-90a","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":33028,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/08\/01\/seek-refuge-entering-masjid\/","url_meta":{"origin":34606,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Seek refuge from Satan when entering mosque","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 1, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: When the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, entered the mosque, he would say, \u201cI seek refuge in Allah Almighty, in his noble countenance, and in his everlasting authority from the accursed Satan.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 466 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37593,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/12\/23\/alternate-dua-salah\/","url_meta":{"origin":34606,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Salat: Alternate opening supplications for prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 23, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Sa\u2019id al-Khudri reported: When the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, performed prayer at night, he would exalt Allah and then say, \u201cGlory be to You, O Allah, with Your praises, blessed is Your name, exalted is Your majesty, and there is no God besides You.\u201d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":1996,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/02\/24\/curse-shaytan-dhikr\/","url_meta":{"origin":34606,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Shaytan: Do not curse Satan, rather mention Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 24, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu al-Malih reported: A man said, \"I was riding on a mount behind the Prophet, and it stumbled, so I said: May Satan perish!\" The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \"Do not say: May Satan perish! If you say that, he will swell with pride until he\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":38541,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2022\/12\/25\/iblees-snout\/","url_meta":{"origin":34606,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Satan: Shaytan withdraws when Allah is remembered","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 25, 2022","format":false,"excerpt":"Mu'adh ibn Jabal reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \"Verily, Satan has a snout like that of a dog positioned over the son of Adam, reminding him of his lusts and his pleasures, bringing him vain hopes and bringing his whisperings to incite doubt\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":2761,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/04\/03\/anger-satan-wudu\/","url_meta":{"origin":34606,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Anger: If you are mad, perform ablution with water","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 3, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"'Atiyyah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace be and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, anger comes from Satan, and Satan was created from fire. Fire is extinguished with water, so if you become angry, perform ablution with water.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 4784 Grade:\u00a0Hasan (fair) according to Ibn Hajar\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32345,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/19\/competing-allah-end-disgrace\/","url_meta":{"origin":34606,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Arrogance: Competing with Allah will end in disgrace","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 19, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cAllah Almighty says: Grandeur is My cloak and pride is My garment. Whoever competes with Me in one of these two, I will throw him into the Hellfire.\u201d Source: Sunan Ibn Ma\u0304jah 4175 Grade: Sahih (authentic)\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/34606","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"auth